Issue on K8s cluster setup manually using vertual machines.

Gernal k8s issues-
1. master node went down
2. Certificate expired
3. Api Server is down/slow.
4. ETCD crashed
5. Schdular is not working.

EKS- AWS will provide you the managed control plane.Once you creat the EKS cluster on AWS.It will work as master node.

AWS fargate-  AWS serverless fargate, you can configure worker node.

Banifites of EKS- No worries about.
1. Certificate expired
2. Api Server is down/slow.
3. ETCD crashed 

Network Service-
1. Cluster IP
2. Nodeport
3. load balancer



